{"tid":2051728,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO 卿姐可否唔好再倒米？","createTime":"2020-06-05T03:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:37:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eefb6cd7860bf81756893ef063e2a1d5575d890e","tid":2051728,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/WK7R2O55DQ3XTWKCLO7NKYCWQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FWK7R2O55DQ3XTWKCLO7NKYCWQA%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EonMh2OwnA7FCi%2BsKpr4SDY%3D&h=9114c69f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FWK7R2O55DQ3XTWKCLO7NKYCWQA%2F&h=b0296d70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/WK7R2O55DQ3XTWKCLO7NKYCWQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n長文自己看，但我好認同:<br />\n<br />\n仲有，呢啲想「當家作主」嘅英國人，對帝國歷史好清楚。不過無絲毫嘅「殖民主義罪疚感」，甚至覺得啲大愛左膠打呢張牌極度反感。我好簡單問您，冇英國佬？今日嘅香港會同湛江或汕頭會有咩分別？您個tone grateful少少得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n英國人會問，呢一代嘅英國人，點解要還佢哋祖先嘅債？而佢哋祖先，以兩次為世界出過力，如果唔係，我哋個個都係講德文同日文啦。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，唔用「殖民主義罪疚感」呢招，用邊招呢？卿姐，您作為多屆票后，您都識點拉啲偏建制游離選民嘅票，想佢所想。您多年來，都有帶嗰種「香港嗰套能振興中華」嘅message。可唔可以實制啲，忍吓自己鍾意點講就點講，有番啲message discipline，諗吓支持脫歐英國人想要啲乜？<br />\n再講，香港人出咗名最大嘅惡習，亦都係英國人最憎嘅嗰樣嘢，就係「老奉」。您封讀者投稿去《泰晤士報》就正正係呢隻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽見有Ｄ人話英國揾工困難無用，駛唔駛養埋你，人地英國年輕人又欠你乜，無好像老奉咁啦"},{"pid":"9aeee01ef35d9a0fbd88143d581f4501bb3cdd13","tid":2051728,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"唔知卿姐拎咩護照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531016dda1b7d5fdddc663d65e5965498ffda35d","tid":2051728,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:00:07.000Z","msg":"<code>最後，我聽到嘅消息係英政府內閣都覺得呢多計劃得民意係五五波。好多支持脫歐嘅英國傳媒工作者，都想凸顯任何來英國嘅人，缺嗰種教養去珍惜做英國人為何物。外來人都係「老奉」心態。刊登卿姐篇文？就係借卿姐把刀，去殺政策。</code><br />\n<br />\n其實都講得啱，都係五五波<br />\n到真係改嘅時候，都會有反對聲音"},{"pid":"cee53713c4430789b80a4986bb095f8fa2527eb0","tid":2051728,"uid":183509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"拜託唔好再重作投稿喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cc733c962315ba16c108d3e824db66027813bd","tid":2051728,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9aeee01ef35d9a0fbd88143d581f4501bb3cdd13","tid":2051728,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"唔知卿姐拎咩護照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"肯定唔會得1本PASSPORT囉"},{"pid":"8b3c818599341959b61f132e01b0b5f8993af7f8","tid":2051728,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"人哋同英國打交道幾十年<br />\n唔好當卿姐傻啦<br />\n有一部分人係真係覺得爭咗香港架"},{"pid":"78c8d66d58b844c873a620bcb5fefae30ddad460","tid":2051728,"uid":170438,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"屌你，英國冇能 cap 油水？"},{"pid":"6427056295eca8671afe5ae10c36caa780fb1e6c","tid":2051728,"uid":59465,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b3c818599341959b61f132e01b0b5f8993af7f8","tid":2051728,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"人哋同英國打交道幾十年<br />\n唔好當卿姐傻啦<br />\n有一部分人係真係覺得爭咗香港架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"佢梗係唔傻<br />\n日日係外國幫手粉飾太平<br />\n周圍同人講香港無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒又入下中聯辦咁<br />\n點會傻呀<br />\n精甩尾就有份"},{"pid":"dae74ece82a4d347f42c3dada2514ec1bdc3a55e","tid":2051728,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9aeee01ef35d9a0fbd88143d581f4501bb3cdd13","tid":2051728,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"唔知卿姐拎咩護照呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha